{"tid":1060663,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紐亞：紅軍後防有好明顯弱點 拜仁有辦法輕鬆應付","createTime":"2019-03-14T01:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T02:45:00.000Z","uid":19552,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b456869289500f57490b513f7899be500830fe09","tid":1060663,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:12:44.000Z","msg":"歐聯16強完成抽籤，上屆亞軍利物浦將大戰拜仁慕尼黑，西甲班霸巴塞隆拿就抽中里昂。巴塞教頭華爾維迪滿意抽籤結果，仲開名話好開心可以避開勁敵利物浦。拜仁門將紐亞需面對埃及文明鋒線，就話紅軍後防有明顯缺點，拜仁一眾出色攻擊手必有理想發揮。<br />\n<br />\n「今季利物浦發揮唔錯，上屆歐聯亦殺入決賽。不過抽正拜仁，紅軍唔會覺得係好籤。佢哋擅於踢反擊足球，埋門觸角亦好犀利，但拜仁已經洞察到佢哋後防有明顯弱點，而且要應付拜仁一眾出色射手。」"},{"pid":"e713ba5117dcd1436046241dfc588d484b02ce81","tid":1060663,"uid":79562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:22:55.000Z","msg":"琴晚邊隊紅色衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243e1e6968ebeb7f9f8ab84a0cdc2c427dfffbaf","tid":1060663,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:24:00.000Z","msg":"蓋狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb6fc27032b585b15bdc2a6dcb8b2bbfbfe463b","tid":1060663,"uid":18276,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:25:54.000Z","msg":"佢咪拜仁個弱點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7372994bb7cfd0cf84c5f2d182e1f212f5317284","tid":1060663,"uid":52524,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"想問下拜仁球員兩回合入左幾多球"},{"pid":"3a417eb1eecd76147ed4d9de4b6ffb2da9f5fd3b","tid":1060663,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"243e1e6968ebeb7f9f8ab84a0cdc2c427dfffbaf","tid":1060663,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:24:00.000Z","msg":"蓋狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"奇狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b204efc97a9716f81d558c